data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, ENF_REF_TO_LEGAL from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'CW'

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, ENF_REF_TO_LEGAL from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadLegalReferralCase
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.STATUS_DATE, T1.STATUS, T1.REFERRAL_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_1, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_2, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_3, T1.REFERRAL_REASON_4, T1.COURT_CASE_NO, T1.TRB_ID, T2.STATUS, T2.STATUS_DATE, T2.CSE_OPEN_DATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_LEGAL_REFERRAL T1 with(readuncommitted) on T2.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER and (T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP between cast(@timestamp1 as datetime2) and cast(@timestamp2 as datetime2)) and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @timestamp2 and ( (T1.STATUS in ('O', 'C', 'S')) and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @timestamp2 or (T1.STATUS in ('W', 'R')) and T1.STATUS_DATE >= @statusDate and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP <= @timestamp2 ) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadServiceProviderCaseAssignment
data.value: select T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.USER_ID, T2.REASON_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.SPD_ID, T2.OFF_ID, T2.OSP_CODE, T2.OSP_DATE, T2.CAS_NO from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_ASSIGN_CASE T2 on @casNo = T2.CAS_NO and T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= cast(@createdTimestamp as date) and T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= cast(@createdTimestamp as date) and T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_ID order by T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set ENF_REF_TO_LEGAL = @enfRefToLegal where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, ENF_REF_TO_LEGAL = @enfRefToLegal where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
